2. Basic Command Line Skills
2.1 Command Line Interface (CLI)
•	A text-based interface used to interact with the os through terminal.
2.2 Basic Navigation and File Commands
•	Check current working directory: pwd
•	List files: ls
•	Create folder: mkdir foldername
•	Move into folder: cd foldername
•	Create file: Touch filename
•	Delete file: rm filename.txt
